\c 6
\s Vanorairwa kuchengeta mirairo yaJehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino iyi mirairo, zvimiso, nemitongo, Jehovha Mwari wenyu yaakaraira kukudzidzisai, kuti muzviite kunyika yamunoyambukira kwairi kuti muigare nhaka\x + 4.1. 5.31. 12.1.\x*;
\v 2 kuti utye Jehovha Mwari wako, kuchengeta zvose zvimiso zvake nemirairo yake, yandinokuraira, iwe, nemwanakomana wako, nemwanakomana wemwanakomana wako, mazuva ose eupenyu hwako\x + 6.13,24. 10.12,13,20. 13.4. Map. 111.10. 128.1. Mup. 12.13.\x*, uye kuti mazuva ako arebeswe\x + 4.40. Zvir. 3.1,2.\x*.
\v 3 Naizvozvo inzwa, Israeri, uye chenjerera ku\add zvi\add*ita, kuti zvikunakire, uye kuti uwande kwazvo\x + 4.40. Zvir. 3.1,2.\x*, Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba ako sezvaakakuvimbisa\x + Gen. 15.5. 22.17.\x*, munyika inoyerera mukaka neuchi\x + Eki. 3.8.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Inzwa, Israeri, Jehovha Mwari wedu ndiJehovha umwe\x + Mako 12.29; Isa. 42.8. Joh. 17.3. 1 VaKori. 8.4,6.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino ude Jehovha Mwari wako nemoyo wako wose uye\x + 10.12. 11.1,13. 30.6. Mat. 22.37. Mako 12.30. Ruk. 10.27.\x* nemweya wako wose uye nesimba rako rose\x + 2 Madz. 23.25.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino mashoko awa andinokuraira nhasi achava mumoyo mako\x + 11.18. 32.46. Map. 37.31. 119.11. Isa. 51.7. Eze. 40.4.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino uchaadzidzisa nekushingaira kuvana vako, uye uchaataura paunenge ugere mumba mako, uye paunenge uchifamba panzira, uye paunenge urere pasi, uye paunenge uchimuka\x + 4.9.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino uchaasungira paruoko rwako kuva chiratidzo; uye achava vundanyara pakati pemeso ako\x + Eki. 13.9. Zvir. 3.3. 6.21. 7.3.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino uchaanyora pamagwatidziro eimba yako uye pamasuwo ako\x + 11.20. Isa. 57.8.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino zvichaitika Jehovha Mwari wako paachakupinza munyika yaakapikira madzibaba ako, kuna Abhurahama, kuna Isaka, uye kuna Jakove, kukupa maguta makuru uye akanaka ausina kuvaka\x + Josh. 11.13. 24.13. Map. 105.44.\x*,
\v 11 nedzimba dzizere nezvakanaka zvose dzausina kuzadza, nematsime akacherwa ausina kuchera, minda yemizambiringa nemiti yemiorivhi yausina kusima; paunenge wadya ukaguta\x + 8.9,10.\x*,
\v 12 zvichenjerere, zvimwe ungakanganwa Jehovha wakakubudisa kubva munyika yeEgipita, muimba yeuranda.
\v 13 Uchatya Jehovha Mwari wako, nekumushumira\x + 6.2. Mat. 4.10. Ruk. 4.8.\x*, uye uchapika nezita rake\x + Map. 63.11. Isa. 45.23. 65.16. Jer. 12.16. Zef. 1.5.\x*.
\v 14 Musatevera vamwe vamwari\x + 8.19. 11.28. Jer. 25.6.\x*, vevamwari vendudzi dzinokupoteredzai\x + 13.7.\x*.
\v 15 Nokuti Jehovha Mwari wako pakati pako ndiMwari ane godo\x + Eki. 20.5.\x*; zvimwe hasha dzaJehovha Mwari wako dzikupfutire, akuparadze ubve pachiso chenyika\x + 7.4. 11.17.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Musaidza Jehovha Mwari wenyu\x + Mat. 4.7. Ruk. 4.12.\x*, sezvamaka\add mu\add*idza paMasa\x + Eki. 17.2,7. 1 VaKori. 10. 9.\x*.
\v 17 Muchachengeta nekushingaira mirairo yaJehovha Mwari wenyu, nezvipupuro zvake, nezvimiso zvake, zvaakakuraira\x + 11.22. Map. 119.4.\x*.
\v 18 Uye uchaita zvakarurama nezvakanaka pameso paJehovha, kuti zvikunakire, uye kuti upinde ugare nhaka yenyika yakanaka, Jehovha Mwari yaakapikira madzibaba ako\x + 4.40.\x*,
\v 19 kudzinga vavengi vako vose kubva pamberi pako, Jehovha sezvaakataura\x + Num. 33.52,53.\x*.
\v 20 Kana mwanakomana wako akakubvunza panguva inouya achiti: Zvii zvipupuro nezvimiso nemitongo Jehovha Mwari wedu zvaakakurairai\x + Eki. 13.14.\x*?
\v 21 Ipapo uchati kumwanakomana wako: Taiva varanda vaFarao muEgipita, Jehovha ndokutibudisa muEgipita neruoko rwune simba\x + 4.34.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino Jehovha wakaita zviratidzo nezvishamiso zvikuru uye zvakaipa muEgipita, kuna Farao nekuimba yake yose pamberi pemeso edu\x + Map. 135.9. Det. 4.34.\x*;
\v 23 asi isu wakatibudisapo kuti atipinze, kutipa nyika yaakapikira kumadzibaba edu.
\v 24 Zvino Jehovha wakatiraira kuita zvose zvimiso izvi, kutya Jehovha Mwari wedu\x + 6.2,13.\x*, kuti zvitinakire mazuva ese\x + 10.13. Jer. 32.39.\x*, kutichengetedza tichirarama sanhasi\x + Map. 41.2. 4.1. 8.1. Rev. 18.5.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino kuchava kururama kwatiri, kana tichichenjerera kuita mirairo yose iyi pamberi paJehovha Mwari wedu, sezvaakatiraira\x + 24.13.\x*.